.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, october, february
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, canadian, british
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the argentine is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is between the argentine and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Birthday   | january        | october | february  | may |
| Nationality      | canadian | turkish  | british | argentine    |

