.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, spanish, russian, argentine
There 4 different types of food: onion, pear, cranberry, corn
1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the argentine is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the argentine is on the far right##1
4. the spanish is the person eating onion##1
5. the russian is between the indian and the spanish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Nationality   | spanish     | russian           | indian | argentine  |
| Food         | onion | corn | pear   | cranberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, chess, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, western, sports, animation
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | card-games   | rock-climbing | collecting | chess      |
| Movie-Genre     | sports | disaster    | western  | animation |

