.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, azalea, balloon-flower, zinnia
City: marseilles, new-york, prague, london
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person traveling to prague##2
3. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Flower       | orchid | zinnia | balloon-flower     | azalea   |
| City   | prague   | new-york     | london | marseilles |

