.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, bridge, whist
There are 4 different nationalities: french, british, egyptian, chinese
1. the person playing bridge is between the french and the person playing chess##2
2. the chinese is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the french is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Game         | snooker | bridge | chess | whist |
| Nationality   | french         | chinese       | british    | egyptian         |

