.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, german, thai, malaysian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, orchid, bellflower
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the malaysian##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the thai##1
3. the polish is on the right of the german##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is between the german and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality    | malaysian   | thai      | german   | polish  |
| Flower   | bellflower | daisy | orchid | amaryllis |

