.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, mauve, light-blue, green
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, december, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes green and the person who likes ebony##2
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Color          | ebony     | mauve | green   | light-blue        |
| Birthday   | april | december   | october | february |

