.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, coral, grey, blue
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, may, february
1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes grey is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Color         | coral | grey | blue | turquise |
| Birthday   | may          | january     | february  | april     |

