.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, rugby, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, taxi, bike
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
3. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Sport           | biathlon | water-polo | tennis | rugby     |
| Transport   | helicopter   | taxi    | bike   | car |

