2. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is tennis##2
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday           | august | october | june | february |
| Sport   | tennis   | volleyball | skateboarding         | cycling |

