.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, funk, electronic, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, taxi, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan funk##1
2. the fan folk is between the person driving the ship and the fan reggae##2
3. the fan funk is on the right of the fan folk##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Music-Genre         | reggae      | folk | funk  | electronic |
| Transport   | taxi | scooter  | ship | trike    |

