2. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person watching musical movies is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person watching animation movies##2
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | animation | musical | crime |
| Sport     | swimming     | rugby   | cricket | basketball  |

