.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
City: marseilles, prague, nizza, miami
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, may, january, november
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person traveling to prague##2
4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| City   | miami | prague | marseilles | nizza |
| Birthday           | january  | november  | may | august      |

