.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, pony, chinchilla
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, sprite, almond-milk
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hamster is between the person drinking cola and the owner of the pony##2
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking cola##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Pet       | chinchilla | hamster | pony | mouse |
| Beverage   | cola    | fanta  | almond-milk    | sprite       |

