.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, havana, bolivar, fonseca
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, dancer, project-manager, designer
1. the dancer is on the left of the designer##1
2. the accountant is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is the accountant##1
4. the designer is between the aristoff-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | aristoff   | havana | bolivar |
| Job         | accountant | dancer | designer     | project-manager    |

