.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, iced-tea, cola
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, oliveros, dannemann, old-henry
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the prince-smoker and the person drinking cola##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | cola     | lemonade | juice |
| Cigar     | oliveros | old-henry | dannemann       | prince     |

 